data.description: WELCOME Home!!! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom house is nestled in a cul-de-sac in the desirable Jubliee community with a large private fenced backyard. You are welcomed by the soaring 2-story foyer with a formal living room and a huge formal dinning room with coffered ceiling. Follow the flowing hardwoods throughout the main level living areas to the exquisite Chef's kitchen with 42" mahogany, Cabinets, kitchen island with and flowing Quartz counter-tops, sleek subway tile backsplash and a walk-in pantry. The kitchen includes a breakfast bar seating for up to four with a breakfast area overlooking the huge sunken family room with coffered ceiling and a half bathroom. Step outside to the backyard and relax on the patio and grilling porch with deck; perfect place to host your next dinner party!     Upstairs features a huge Primary Owner's Suite with trey ceilings all leading to the Primary Ensuite showcasing double vanities, garden tub, separate tiled shower with a huge walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms, Jack and Jill bathroom and a spacious laundry room. Upgrades includes all hardwood floors on the main level, 6ft privacy fence, EV (Electric Vehicle) wired charge in the garage, and deck. Don't miss the opportunity to move in this year!  **NEW BUYER INCENTIVE: Seller paying closing costs of $5,000 with full list price plus Lender credit up to $2,500 towards Buyer's closing costs if using preferred Lender.**
